{"tid":1171405,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「北美事務協調委員會」改名「台灣美國事務委員會」　台外交部：象徵台美關係緊密","createTime":"2019-05-25T16:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T23:31:49.000Z","uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f3a6d7b683bda2239cba875bbcc1ed79ce872006","tid":1171405,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T16:25:13.000Z","msg":"「北美事務協調委員會」改名「台灣美國事務委員會」　台外交部：象徵台美關係緊密<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20190525/s00004/1558773043652/%e3%80%8c%e5%8c%97%e7%be%8e%e4%ba%8b%e5%8b%99%e5%8d%94%e8%aa%bf%e5%a7%94%e5%93%a1%e6%9c%83%e3%80%8d%e6%94%b9%e5%90%8d%e3%80%8c%e5%8f%b0%e7%81%a3%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e4%ba%8b%e5%8b%99%e5%a7%94%e5%93%a1%e6%9c%83%e3%80%8d-%e5%8f%b0%e5%a4%96%e4%ba%a4%e9%83%a8-%e8%b1%a1%e5%be%b5%e5%8f%b0%e7%be%8e%e9%97%9c%e4%bf%82%e7%b7%8a%e5%af%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20190525%2Fs00004%2F1558773043652%2F%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%258c%2597%25e7%25be%258e%25e4%25ba%258b%25e5%258b%2599%25e5%258d%2594%25e8%25aa%25bf%25e5%25a7%2594%25e5%2593%25a1%25e6%259c%2583%25e3%2580%258d%25e6%2594%25b9%25e5%2590%258d%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%258f%25b0%25e7%2581%25a3%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e4%25ba%258b%25e5%258b%2599%25e5%25a7%2594%25e5%2593%25a1%25e6%259c%2583%25e3%2580%258d-%25e5%258f%25b0%25e5%25a4%2596%25e4%25ba%25a4%25e9%2583%25a8-%25e8%25b1%25a1%25e5%25be%25b5%25e5%258f%25b0%25e7%25be%258e%25e9%2597%259c%25e4%25bf%2582%25e7%25b7%258a%25e5%25af%2586&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFD%2BQayrLlxBj8%2BPX1Ib8Zww%3D&h=3c143b35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20190525%2Fs00004%2F1558773043652%2F%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%258c%2597%25e7%25be%258e%25e4%25ba%258b%25e5%258b%2599%25e5%258d%2594%25e8%25aa%25bf%25e5%25a7%2594%25e5%2593%25a1%25e6%259c%2583%25e3%2580%258d%25e6%2594%25b9%25e5%2590%258d%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%258f%25b0%25e7%2581%25a3%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e4%25ba%258b%25e5%258b%2599%25e5%25a7%2594%25e5%2593%25a1%25e6%259c%2583%25e3%2580%258d-%25e5%258f%25b0%25e5%25a4%2596%25e4%25ba%25a4%25e9%2583%25a8-%25e8%25b1%25a1%25e5%25be%25b5%25e5%258f%25b0%25e7%25be%258e%25e9%2597%259c%25e4%25bf%2582%25e7%25b7%258a%25e5%25af%2586&h=b40e34c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20190525/s00004/1558773043652/%e3%80%8c%e5%8c%97%e7%be%8e%e4%ba%8b%e5%8b%99%e5%8d%94%e8%aa%bf%e5%a7%94%e5%93%a1%e6%9c%83%e3%80%8d%e6%94%b9%e5%90%8d%e3%80%8c%e5%8f%b0%e7%81%a3%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e4%ba%8b%e5%8b%99%e5%a7%94%e5%93%a1%e6%9c%83%e3%80%8d-%e5%8f%b0%e5%a4%96%e4%ba%a4%e9%83%a8-%e8%b1%a1%e5%be%b5%e5%8f%b0%e7%be%8e%e9%97%9c%e4%bf%82%e7%b7%8a%e5%af%86</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣外交部今日（25日）宣布，為明確反映台灣處理對美國事務代表機構的工作內涵，經過與美方充分協調溝通後，決定將「北美事務協調委員會」，改名為「台灣美國事務委員會」，象徵台美關係緊密。<br />\n<br />\n台灣總統蔡英文稱，改名不僅見證了台美關係穩固，也代表國際社會對台灣的支持一定會愈來愈多。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人表示，「台灣美國事務委員會」更能反映協調美國相關事務的角色，而非更廣泛的北美事務。不過，發言人同時重申，美國依據美中三公報與《台灣關係法》的一中政策並未改變。<br />\n<br />\n中央社引述消息報道，改名仍須經過台灣的行政程序，程序完成後，將舉行揭牌儀式。<br />\n<br />\n台灣外交部表示，美國依據1979年台灣關係法的規定，成立美國在台協會（American Institute in Taiwan，AIT），作為執行美國政府與台灣相關事務的代表機構，台灣相應地於同年設立「北美事務協調委員會」，作為美國在台協會的對等機構。<br />\n<br />\n（中央社）"},{"pid":"c2370acce4472dfa1f385ff877e904349f888178","tid":1171405,"uid":15730,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"近期啲新聞睇到我好high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01277f6423cdc88961e5913d0b3ab36951dac92","tid":1171405,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2370acce4472dfa1f385ff877e904349f888178","tid":1171405,"uid":15730,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"近期啲新聞睇到我好high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.